<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 06:12:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾就南海主张斥责中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-rebukes-china-over-south-china-sea-claims-2023-12-20/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周三斥责中国指责菲律宾在南海挑起紧张局势并煽动麻烦，称只有北京相信其所说的话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 05:58:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-rebukes-china-over-south-china-sea-claims-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>台湾将根据威胁程度“处理”大量中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-handle-spate-chinese-balloons-based-threat-level-2023-12-20/</link><description>台湾国防部周三表示，台湾将根据威胁评估“处理”在附近飞行的中国热气球，不过官员们认为当前的热气球是出于天气目的，由每年这个时候的盛行风驱动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 04:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-handle-spate-chinese-balloons-based-threat-level-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>尼加拉瓜升级与中国关系，在西方制裁中寻求财政支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nicaragua-upgrades-ties-with-china-seeks-financial-support-amid-western-2023-12-20/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中国和尼加拉瓜周三升级了双边关系，向受制裁的中美洲政府提供经济支持，并进一步推进北京在美国后院的战略野心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 04:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nicaragua-upgrades-ties-with-china-seeks-financial-support-amid-western-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国救援人员冒着严寒寻找地震幸存者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-rescuers-brave-freezing-cold-find-earthquake-survivors-2023-12-20/</link><description>周三，数千名救援人员冒着低于零度的条件，面临着艰巨的任务，寻找和治疗一天多前发生在中国西北部甘肃省偏远地区的强烈地震的幸存者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 03:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-rescuers-brave-freezing-cold-find-earthquake-survivors-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>李氏家族将通过交易走出价值陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/li-clan-will-deal-their-way-out-value-trap-2023-12-20/</link><description>亚洲最初的大亨李嘉诚在近十年前瓜分其香港帝国时皈依了股东信仰。尽管投资者支持这笔交易，但随着中美紧张局势加剧，他们很快对该公司失去了信心。解决价值难题将是他的儿子李泽钜2024年的首要任务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 02:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/li-clan-will-deal-their-way-out-value-trap-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国维持贷款基准利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-lending-benchmark-rates-unchanged-expected-2023-12-20/</link><description>市场观察人士预计，北京将在新的一年进一步实施货币宽松政策。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 01:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-lending-benchmark-rates-unchanged-expected-2023-12-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国零售商战略转变可能加剧通货紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shift-chinese-retailers-strategy-risks-entrenching-deflation-2023-12-19/</link><description>中国零售商转向低价商品和服务以赢得注重成本的消费者的战略转变，有可能使中国近期的通货紧缩趋势更永久地融入到这个世界第二大经济体中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 23:07:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shift-chinese-retailers-strategy-risks-entrenching-deflation-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国将13家中国企业列入未经核实名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-adds-13-companies-china-unverified-list-2023-12-19/</link><description>根据周二发布的政府通知，美国已将 13 家中国公司列入接收美国出口产品的实体名单，但官员无法对其进行检查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 14:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-adds-13-companies-china-unverified-list-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>全球10大钢铁企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/worlds-top-10-steelmakers-2023-12-19/</link><description>日本新日铁周一达成协议，将以 149 亿美元现金收购美国钢铁公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 08:56:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/worlds-top-10-steelmakers-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国暂停制裁后，中化集团购买稀有的委内瑞拉石油船货--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-sinochem-buys-rare-venezuelan-oil-cargo-after-us-suspends-sanctions-2023-12-19/</link><description>中国中化集团公司已购买了100万桶委内瑞拉原油，将于12月抵达，这在这家国有石油和化工集团利用华盛顿暂停对这家南美生产商实施制裁的机会之际进行了罕见的购买。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 05:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-sinochem-buys-rare-venezuelan-oil-cargo-after-us-suspends-sanctions-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港民主人士黎智英的安全审判面临外交压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/diplomatic-pressure-builds-over-hong-kong-democrat-jimmy-lais-security-trial-2023-12-19/</link><description>国际压力正在因香港对中国主要批评者黎智英进行的具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判而增加，随着周二审判进入第二天，英国当局要求领事探视这位被监禁的民主党人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 04:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/diplomatic-pressure-builds-over-hong-kong-democrat-jimmy-lais-security-trial-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>抛开紧张局势，台湾总统在致命地震后向中国提供援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/setting-aside-tensions-taiwan-president-offers-aid-china-after-deadly-quake-2023-12-19/</link><description>青藏高原北部边缘发生地震，造成100多人死亡，台湾总统蔡英文周二向中国表示哀悼，并向中国政府提供帮助。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 03:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/setting-aside-tensions-taiwan-president-offers-aid-china-after-deadly-quake-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统称与中国的外交努力“走向糟糕”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-diplomatic-efforts-with-china-heading-poor-direction-2023-12-19/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，菲律宾处理南海问题的方式需要“范式转​​变”，因为与北京的外交努力“朝着糟糕的方向发展”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-diplomatic-efforts-with-china-heading-poor-direction-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告另一个疑似中国气象气球穿越台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-another-suspected-chinese-weather-balloon-crossing-taiwan-strait-2023-12-19/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，一个疑似中国气象气球周一飞越敏感的台湾海峡，但仍停留在台湾以北的地方，这是本月台北第三次报告称气球在附近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 01:30:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-another-suspected-chinese-weather-balloon-crossing-taiwan-strait-2023-12-19/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国经济能否重回正轨？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/can-china-get-its-economic-miracle-back-track-2024-2023-12-18/</link><description>中国在新冠疫情后令人失望的复苏让人对其数十年惊人增长的基础产生了重大怀疑，并给北京带来了2024年及以后的艰难选择：承担更多债务还是减少增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 23:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/can-china-get-its-economic-miracle-back-track-2024-2023-12-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>